1
00:00:00,810 --> 00:00:03,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's finally time for Osaka High's
 school festival!</font>

2
00:00:03,980 --> 00:00:08,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font size="20">{\an4}<font color="#808279">School Festival</font></font></b></font></font>

3
00:00:05,270 --> 00:00:06,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You listening, punks?!</font>

4
00:00:06,820 --> 00:00:08,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give this all you've got!</font>

5
00:00:08,270 --> 00:00:10,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sir!</font>

6
00:00:10,730 --> 00:00:13,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's like everyone's going 
to war or something.</font>

7
00:00:14,640 --> 00:00:15,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, yeah.</font>

8
00:00:15,500 --> 00:00:17,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was intimidated by it all
 as a first-year too,</font>

9
00:00:17,770 --> 00:00:19,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but our school festival is hot stuff.</font>

10
00:00:20,590 --> 00:00:23,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is new for the first-years, 
so pay attention.</font>

11
00:00:24,190 --> 00:00:26,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Osaka's school festival
 lasts for three days.</font>

12
00:00:26,910 --> 00:00:29,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Day one features athletic events.</font>

13
00:00:29,040 --> 00:00:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Day two hosts festival activities indoors.</font>

14
00:00:31,380 --> 00:00:34,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And on day three, we open 
the campus to outside guests.</font>

15
00:00:34,470 --> 00:00:36,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So to boil it all down,</font>

16
00:00:36,140 --> 00:00:39,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we're basically jamming together 
our field day and cultural festival.</font>

17
00:00:40,920 --> 00:00:42,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That sounds like a ton of fun.</font>

18
00:00:42,520 --> 00:00:44,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this is the important part!</font>

19
00:00:44,640 --> 00:00:48,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our festival pits the dorms 
against each other for the grand title!</font>

20
00:00:49,610 --> 00:00:51,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The dorms compete against each other?!</font>

21
00:02:22,590 --> 00:02:26,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As you are all aware, our school splits 
each grade level into three classes.</font>

22
00:02:26,710 --> 00:02:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Said classes are then assigned to dorms.</font>

23
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:32,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="36"><font color="#401f4e">Dorm 1</font></font></font></font>

24
00:02:29,410 --> 00:02:32,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In Dorm 1, we have students 
focused on sports.</font>

25
00:02:32,940 --> 00:02:35,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="36"><font color="#401f4e">Dorm 3</font></font></font></font>

26
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:35,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In Dorm 3, we have students 
focused on the arts.</font>

27
00:02:35,550 --> 00:02:39,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="36"><font color="#401f4e">Dorm 2</font></font></font></font>

28
00:02:36,300 --> 00:02:39,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And our dorm, Dorm 2, has a mix 
of students from sports and the arts.</font>

29
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:43,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The overall winner is determined
 by how many points each dorm gets.</font>

30
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:47,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't forget that this is riding 
on each one of you individually!</font>

31
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:50,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, and I forgot something important.</font>

32
00:02:50,910 --> 00:02:54,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The winning dorm gets special 
privileges as their reward.</font>

33
00:02:54,250 --> 00:02:55,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Special privileges?</font>

34
00:02:55,900 --> 00:02:59,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For example, special meals
 in the dining hall.</font>

35
00:02:59,150 --> 00:03:01,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Special meals?!</font>

36
00:03:01,070 --> 00:03:06,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rumor has it they get a full-course
 French dinner once a month.</font>

37
00:03:06,860 --> 00:03:07,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really?</font>

38
00:03:08,330 --> 00:03:13,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Additionally, the class who earns the
 most points will be named the MVPs...</font>

39
00:03:14,980 --> 00:03:16,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and score a cash prize.</font>

40
00:03:16,420 --> 00:03:18,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Cash prize!</font>

41
00:03:20,070 --> 00:03:23,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All right, if they weren't 
fired up after all that,</i></font>

42
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:25,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>we wouldn't stand a chance of winning.</i></font>

43
00:03:26,200 --> 00:03:29,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The team leader for each dorm
 will be the RA, so me.</font>

44
00:03:29,610 --> 00:03:31,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's keep our eyes on the prize and—</font>

45
00:03:33,060 --> 00:03:35,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not gonna happen, Dorm 2 dwellers!</font>

46
00:03:35,920 --> 00:03:39,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This year, Dorm 1 is taking that prize!</font>

47
00:03:39,690 --> 00:03:40,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

48
00:03:40,570 --> 00:03:43,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The annoying crew showed up.</font>

49
00:03:43,150 --> 00:03:44,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you're awake now.</font>

50
00:03:44,630 --> 00:03:45,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who is that?</font>

51
00:03:45,820 --> 00:03:48,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If it isn't the karate chump.</font>

52
00:03:48,000 --> 00:03:50,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who're you calling a karate chump?!</font>

53
00:03:50,450 --> 00:03:53,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's Tennoji Megumi, Dorm 1's RA.</font>

54
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:56,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's also the captain 
of our monstrous karate team.</font>

55
00:03:56,460 --> 00:03:58,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nanba Minami!</font>

56
00:03:58,720 --> 00:04:02,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like the time to settle 
our score has finally come!</font>

57
00:04:02,480 --> 00:04:04,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Victory shall be ours!</font>

58
00:04:04,180 --> 00:04:05,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

59
00:04:05,390 --> 00:04:09,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, we can't exactly 
roll over and let you win.</font>

60
00:04:12,730 --> 00:04:14,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You can see the sparks flying!</i></font>

61
00:04:16,400 --> 00:04:17,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, hey, Sano.</font>

62
00:04:17,920 --> 00:04:20,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are those two guys in the back?</font>

63
00:04:20,420 --> 00:04:24,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, they're two of what
 they call their "Big Four."</font>

64
00:04:24,690 --> 00:04:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On the right is Kitahanada, a second-year.</font>

65
00:04:27,290 --> 00:04:29,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On the left is Kujo, 
their vice captain and a third-year.</font>

66
00:04:30,940 --> 00:04:35,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They call him both "Bodhisattva Kujo"
 and "Asura Kujo."</font>

67
00:04:35,590 --> 00:04:38,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not the kind of guy you wanna tangle with.</font>

68
00:04:40,670 --> 00:04:43,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He seems nice, though.</i></font>

69
00:04:47,470 --> 00:04:48,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What was that?</i></font>

70
00:04:50,010 --> 00:04:52,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This year, we're claiming victory.</font>

71
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:54,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You will taste the bitter
 nectar of defeat!</font>

72
00:04:54,730 --> 00:04:56,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, let us impose no more!</font>

73
00:04:56,500 --> 00:04:57,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're off!</font>

74
00:04:57,450 --> 00:04:58,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

75
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:03,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's just say that was a demonstration.</font>

76
00:05:03,610 --> 00:05:05,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pay them no mind.</font>

77
00:05:05,180 --> 00:05:06,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We've gotten off track,</font>

78
00:05:06,680 --> 00:05:12,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but remember what what we win in
the festival will change our lives here.</font>

79
00:05:12,010 --> 00:05:12,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is all.</font>

80
00:05:12,950 --> 00:05:18,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, and as usual, we will also be holding 
our regular Miss Osaka beauty pageant.</font>

81
00:05:18,170 --> 00:05:19,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a beauty pageant?</font>

82
00:05:19,760 --> 00:05:21,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can nominate yourself or others,</font>

83
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:24,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so if you're even a little easy
 on the eyes, step up.</font>

84
00:05:28,030 --> 00:05:31,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The school festival sounds like a lot.</font>

85
00:05:32,060 --> 00:05:33,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whaddaya mean?</font>

86
00:05:33,080 --> 00:05:34,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't think it sounds fun?</font>

87
00:05:34,170 --> 00:05:37,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, you could say it's a lot, yeah.</font>

88
00:05:37,140 --> 00:05:39,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's not without its merits.</font>

89
00:05:39,270 --> 00:05:40,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

90
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:42,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Cause girls are gonna be coming!</font>

91
00:05:42,810 --> 00:05:44,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Real, actual girls!</font>

92
00:05:44,110 --> 00:05:47,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right! On day three,
they'll be here in droves!</font>

93
00:05:48,230 --> 00:05:49,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, are you in, Ashiya?</font>

94
00:05:49,770 --> 00:05:50,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean?</font>

95
00:05:50,750 --> 00:05:52,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You gonna enter the beauty pageant?</font>

96
00:05:53,520 --> 00:05:56,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, Nakao won last year.</font>

97
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:58,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why the hell would I do that?!</font>

98
00:05:58,240 --> 00:06:02,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why would I go out of my way to enter 
a competition that could expose me?</i></font>

99
00:06:02,850 --> 00:06:04,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Saw that coming.</i></font>

100
00:06:05,070 --> 00:06:07,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Aw, Mizuki isn't going to enter?</i></font>

101
00:06:07,550 --> 00:06:10,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an9}<font face="Impact"><font size="22"><font color="#44a886">I Don't Look Good
 in Women's Clothing!</font></font></font></font>

102
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:12,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, good night.</font>

103
00:06:12,550 --> 00:06:13,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Night!</font>

104
00:06:14,450 --> 00:06:15,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See you tomorrow.</font>

105
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:20,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Mizuki in girls' clothes, huh?</i></font>

106
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:26,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nakatsu.</font>

107
00:06:29,070 --> 00:06:31,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's crazy cute!</i></font>

108
00:06:31,650 --> 00:06:33,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pervert.</font>

109
00:06:33,120 --> 00:06:35,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your aura is turning pink.</font>

110
00:06:35,450 --> 00:06:36,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you in love?</font>

111
00:06:37,380 --> 00:06:40,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what kind of events
 happen on the first day?</font>

112
00:06:41,180 --> 00:06:44,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stuff like a 500-meter relay,</font>

113
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:46,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">an obstacle course, a scavenger hunt,</font>

114
00:06:46,990 --> 00:06:49,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a chicken fight, and swimming, I think.</font>

115
00:06:52,160 --> 00:06:54,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd better not enter the chicken fight.</font>

116
00:06:54,880 --> 00:06:56,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

117
00:06:58,120 --> 00:07:00,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you seriously asking that?</font>

118
00:07:00,350 --> 00:07:02,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What even is a chicken fight?</font>

119
00:07:03,660 --> 00:07:06,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whatever. Just go to sleep already.</font>

120
00:07:06,360 --> 00:07:08,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's a chicken fight?</font>

121
00:07:08,500 --> 00:07:10,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you won't tell me, I'll...</font>

122
00:07:10,660 --> 00:07:12,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">tickle you!</font>

123
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:15,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You doofus, stop it.</font>

124
00:07:15,700 --> 00:07:17,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wish!</font>

125
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:18,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You little...</font>

126
00:07:26,380 --> 00:07:29,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sheesh! Stop fooling around.</font>

127
00:07:29,130 --> 00:07:30,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get to bed.</font>

128
00:07:30,850 --> 00:07:33,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yeah, good night.</font>

129
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:34,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

130
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:38,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That caught me off guard.</i></font>

131
00:07:39,200 --> 00:07:42,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Makes me think of what happened 
 at our summer job...</i></font>

132
00:07:43,340 --> 00:07:47,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Back then, Sano held me in that grove.</i></font>

133
00:07:47,570 --> 00:07:50,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I even had a dream that we kissed.</i></font>

134
00:07:51,950 --> 00:07:55,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I mean, it was an accident,
but we </i>have<i> kissed before.</i></font>

135
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:58,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I still remember what his lips felt like.</i></font>

136
00:08:03,950 --> 00:08:06,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The feel of his shoulders and back...</i></font>

137
00:08:06,710 --> 00:08:07,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The warmth of his arms...</i></font>

138
00:08:09,010 --> 00:08:10,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The heartbeat in his chest...</i></font>

139
00:08:11,330 --> 00:08:13,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My body remembers it all.</i></font>

140
00:08:14,470 --> 00:08:16,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My heart just flutters.</i></font>

141
00:08:17,150 --> 00:08:19,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Everywhere he touched me feels so warm.</i></font>

142
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:23,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I guess I like him just that much.</i></font>

143
00:08:24,170 --> 00:08:26,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Do I just want to be around her?</i></font>

144
00:08:30,260 --> 00:08:31,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I...</i></font>

145
00:08:34,420 --> 00:08:36,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rock, paper, scissors!</font>

146
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="8"><font face="Arial"><font color="#98b9ac"><b><Indoors>
Swimming
Dodgeball</b></font></font></font></font>

147
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="8"><font face="Arial"><font color="#98b9ac"><b><Outdoors>
2,000 m relay 500 m relay
Obstacle course Chicken fight</b></font></font></font></font>

148
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Awesome!</font>

149
00:08:39,620 --> 00:08:41,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you two are in 
the chicken fight as well!</font>

150
00:08:41,620 --> 00:08:44,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you to steer clear of this event.</font>

151
00:08:41,640 --> 00:08:48,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="8"><font face="Arial"><font color="#98b9ac"><b><Indoors>
Swimming
Dodgeball</b></font></font></font></font>

152
00:08:41,640 --> 00:08:48,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="8"><font face="Arial"><font color="#98b9ac"><b><Outdoors>
2,000 m relay 500 m relay
Obstacle course Chicken fight</b></font></font></font></font>

153
00:08:44,020 --> 00:08:45,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll be fine! Just fine!</font>

154
00:08:45,730 --> 00:08:48,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm light, so I won't get caught!</font>

155
00:08:48,860 --> 00:08:51,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's not what I meant.</i></font>

156
00:08:51,630 --> 00:08:53,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, Nakatsu!</font>

157
00:08:53,200 --> 00:08:54,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's do this!</font>

158
00:08:54,270 --> 00:08:55,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You bet!</font>

159
00:08:55,260 --> 00:08:56,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya!</font>

160
00:08:56,530 --> 00:08:58,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nakao-kun?</font>

161
00:08:58,860 --> 00:09:00,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll enter the pageant, right?</font>

162
00:09:00,260 --> 00:09:02,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll be our runner-up for sure!</font>

163
00:09:02,880 --> 00:09:03,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not entering.</font>

164
00:09:04,710 --> 00:09:06,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why not?!</font>

165
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:08,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't look good in women's clothing.</font>

166
00:09:08,340 --> 00:09:12,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you think anyone here
 would look better than us?</font>

167
00:09:12,770 --> 00:09:16,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I, er... th-think they'd do fine.</font>

168
00:09:16,560 --> 00:09:19,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I really can't enter the pageant!</i></font>

169
00:09:20,380 --> 00:09:22,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's this, Ashiya? You're not entering?</font>

170
00:09:22,980 --> 00:09:24,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nanba-senpai!</font>

171
00:09:24,960 --> 00:09:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The pageant is very important for us.</font>

172
00:09:27,530 --> 00:09:30,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't forget that cash prize. <i>Cash prize</i>!</font>

173
00:09:30,130 --> 00:09:32,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya, please enter!</font>

174
00:09:32,000 --> 00:09:33,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You could do it for sure!</font>

175
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:38,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Cash prize! Cash prize! Cash prize!</font>

176
00:09:35,670 --> 00:09:38,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Everyone's lost their minds 
about the cash prize.</i></font>

177
00:09:38,050 --> 00:09:39,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, it's settled.</font>

178
00:09:41,340 --> 00:09:43,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>N-No way!</i></font>

179
00:09:44,150 --> 00:09:46,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nakatsu, your aura is pink.</font>

180
00:09:46,730 --> 00:09:47,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch yourself, man.</font>

181
00:09:47,820 --> 00:09:49,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-My bad.</font>

182
00:09:49,060 --> 00:09:53,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, the pageant isn't
 the only thing I'm here about.</font>

183
00:09:54,030 --> 00:09:57,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On the final day, we've got the 
time-honored 2,000-meter relay from hell,</font>

184
00:09:57,980 --> 00:10:01,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">which is worth enough points to make
 or break the entire competition.</font>

185
00:10:01,070 --> 00:10:03,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a relay on the final day too?</font>

186
00:10:03,760 --> 00:10:07,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a five-man event, with each 
runner taking 400 meters.</font>

187
00:10:07,250 --> 00:10:09,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's pretty tough.
A lot of responsibility.</font>

188
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:12,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To keep our participants'
 identities secret,</font>

189
00:10:12,060 --> 00:10:13,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will be picking the runners myself.</font>

190
00:10:13,850 --> 00:10:15,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is not up for debate.</font>

191
00:10:15,490 --> 00:10:16,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's a demon!</i></font>

192
00:10:18,320 --> 00:10:20,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soft! You're soft! You're all soft!</font>

193
00:10:21,310 --> 00:10:22,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These guys again?</font>

194
00:10:22,490 --> 00:10:24,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">God, you're annoying.</font>

195
00:10:24,470 --> 00:10:27,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Scheme all you want!
 It won't do you any good!</font>

196
00:10:27,170 --> 00:10:29,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no way you guys can win.</font>

197
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:30,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

198
00:10:30,800 --> 00:10:31,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This year for sure...</font>

199
00:10:31,830 --> 00:10:34,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This year, victory's going to Dorm 1!</font>

200
00:10:34,610 --> 00:10:36,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you know what, Nanba Minami?!</font>

201
00:10:36,620 --> 00:10:39,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once we win, I'm going
to cut off all your hair!</font>

202
00:10:39,490 --> 00:10:41,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave my hair out of this.</font>

203
00:10:41,850 --> 00:10:44,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your stupid, flashy mop
 makes me wanna puke!</font>

204
00:10:45,330 --> 00:10:48,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's rich from the dorm 
that bombs the pageant every year!</font>

205
00:10:48,370 --> 00:10:49,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut your mouth, whelp!</font>

206
00:10:49,920 --> 00:10:51,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eek! Senpai!</font>

207
00:10:52,780 --> 00:10:54,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Speaking of the pageant,</font>

208
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:57,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">yes, it's true that we used 
to struggle every year,</font>

209
00:10:57,270 --> 00:10:58,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but no longer!</font>

210
00:10:58,380 --> 00:10:59,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kadoma!</font>

211
00:10:59,550 --> 00:11:00,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here!</font>

212
00:11:01,870 --> 00:11:02,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-He's cute!</font>

213
00:11:02,940 --> 00:11:03,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way!</font>

214
00:11:03,670 --> 00:11:05,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This can't be happening!</font>

215
00:11:05,100 --> 00:11:07,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You get it now, you dolts?!</font>

216
00:11:08,940 --> 00:11:10,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Captain, I need to tell you something.</font>

217
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:13,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That kid over there? He's their...</font>

218
00:11:14,390 --> 00:11:15,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it's you!</font>

219
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:17,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya Mizuki in the flesh.</font>

220
00:11:19,820 --> 00:11:21,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've got a face like a girl.</font>

221
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:25,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looking at you, I have my doubts
 about the rumors of your leg strength.</font>

222
00:11:25,330 --> 00:11:28,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe you're only good 
for the pageant after all.</font>

223
00:11:29,110 --> 00:11:32,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't put me down. 
I'm also entering the chicken fight.</font>

224
00:11:32,540 --> 00:11:33,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The chicken fight?</font>

225
00:11:33,810 --> 00:11:35,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't make me laugh.</font>

226
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:36,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A little shrimp like you is just</font>

227
00:11:36,930 --> 00:11:40,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">going to get hurt and run home 
with your tail between your legs.</font>

228
00:11:43,260 --> 00:11:45,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't know that before we compete!</font>

229
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:49,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I am <i>not</i> gonna lose to someone
who judges based on appearances!</font>

230
00:11:49,410 --> 00:11:50,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It just had to go there...</i></font>

231
00:11:51,130 --> 00:11:52,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine then.</font>

232
00:11:52,250 --> 00:11:54,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's on in the chicken fight, you brat!</font>

233
00:11:54,830 --> 00:11:56,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take you down!</font>

234
00:11:57,940 --> 00:11:59,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><b><font color="#878789">Infirmary</font></b></font></font>

235
00:11:59,890 --> 00:12:01,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You? In the chicken fight?</font>

236
00:12:01,510 --> 00:12:02,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that a good idea?</font>

237
00:12:02,700 --> 00:12:05,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, not you too!</font>

238
00:12:05,920 --> 00:12:08,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, do your best.</font>

239
00:12:09,810 --> 00:12:11,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry I'm late!</font>

240
00:12:11,840 --> 00:12:13,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Io-san!</font>

241
00:12:13,200 --> 00:12:16,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, it feels like forever, Mizuki-kun!</font>

242
00:12:16,220 --> 00:12:16,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it.</font>

243
00:12:16,990 --> 00:12:19,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you not use my office
for your little meet-up?</font>

244
00:12:19,710 --> 00:12:21,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You say something, Hokuto?</font>

245
00:12:21,580 --> 00:12:23,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-Not a peep, my dear sister!</font>

246
00:12:24,090 --> 00:12:26,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look, I finished your vest.</font>

247
00:12:26,880 --> 00:12:29,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, thank you so much!</font>

248
00:12:29,660 --> 00:12:30,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's soft wire inside,</font>

249
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so you'll look completely
 flat from outside.</font>

250
00:12:33,540 --> 00:12:34,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i></i>Completely<i> flat, huh?</i></font>

251
00:12:35,600 --> 00:12:38,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, you're entering the pageant?</font>

252
00:12:38,410 --> 00:12:41,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I kinda got strong-armed into it.</font>

253
00:12:41,010 --> 00:12:42,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Minami was in it too.</font>

254
00:12:42,880 --> 00:12:44,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That takes me back.</font>

255
00:12:44,070 --> 00:12:46,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, N-Nanba-senpai entered?</font>

256
00:12:46,240 --> 00:12:48,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back when he was a first-year.</font>

257
00:12:49,450 --> 00:12:50,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look.</font>

258
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:52,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, wow! He's so gorgeous.</font>

259
00:12:52,930 --> 00:12:54,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?!</font>

260
00:12:54,060 --> 00:12:55,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was that year's Miss Osaka.</font>

261
00:12:55,870 --> 00:12:57,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He looks just like you.</font>

262
00:12:57,440 --> 00:12:59,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like mother, like son!</font>

263
00:13:00,280 --> 00:13:02,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gorgeous? I'm gorgeous!</font>

264
00:13:02,420 --> 00:13:06,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really, and just like him, you get 
more shameless every year.</font>

265
00:13:10,760 --> 00:13:12,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wasn't expecting that!</i></font>

266
00:13:12,160 --> 00:13:15,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who would've thought that
 Nanba-senpai was Miss Osaka?</i></font>

267
00:13:16,690 --> 00:13:18,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Speak of the devil!</i></font>

268
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:22,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nanba-senpai...</font>

269
00:13:26,080 --> 00:13:29,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've never seen him like this before.</i></font>

270
00:13:30,660 --> 00:13:32,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right!</font>

271
00:13:33,420 --> 00:13:35,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sano and Nakatsu got put in basketball,</font>

272
00:13:35,170 --> 00:13:37,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">while I got put in volleyball,</font>

273
00:13:37,040 --> 00:13:38,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but let's all do our best!</font>

274
00:13:38,170 --> 00:13:40,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're really fired up, huh, Mizuki?</font>

275
00:13:40,640 --> 00:13:41,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course!</font>

276
00:13:41,950 --> 00:13:44,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}This is how we're gonna fight back!</font>

277
00:13:43,130 --> 00:13:46,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That squirt? He's who 
we're supposed to watch out for?</font>

278
00:13:46,190 --> 00:13:49,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He does seem especially fast.</font>

279
00:13:49,260 --> 00:13:50,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an7}<font face="Arial"><font size="14"><font color="#3c3c40"><b>Don't let Ashiya Mizuki 
from 2-C out of your sight</b></font></font></font></font>

280
00:13:50,890 --> 00:13:54,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya Mizuki, huh?</font>

281
00:13:59,670 --> 00:14:00,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Izumi!</font>

282
00:14:08,380 --> 00:14:10,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's in!</font>

283
00:14:11,140 --> 00:14:14,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya, it's nearly time
 for our volleyball match.</font>

284
00:14:14,060 --> 00:14:15,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Already?</font>

285
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:17,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this is the finals!</font>

286
00:14:17,180 --> 00:14:18,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, let's go.</font>

287
00:14:19,920 --> 00:14:21,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you know...</font>

288
00:14:21,790 --> 00:14:23,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nakatsu's feral, so that was his usual,</font>

289
00:14:23,920 --> 00:14:25,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but Sano's pretty good, huh?</font>

290
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:28,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's not even on the team,
 and he's that skilled.</font>

291
00:14:28,650 --> 00:14:31,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He had the third-years
 on the other team scrambling.</font>

292
00:14:31,760 --> 00:14:34,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess it's his jumping power!</font>

293
00:14:34,310 --> 00:14:35,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right!</font>

294
00:14:36,010 --> 00:14:39,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya, you perk right up 
whenever Sano's involved.</font>

295
00:14:39,360 --> 00:14:40,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do I?</font>

296
00:14:40,870 --> 00:14:42,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all over your face.</font>

297
00:14:44,490 --> 00:14:49,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And the winner of the basketball 
tournament is Dorm 2's class 2-C!</i></font>

298
00:14:49,450 --> 00:14:50,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Awesome!</font>

299
00:14:55,240 --> 00:14:56,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nanba-senpai!</font>

300
00:14:57,440 --> 00:14:59,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We won the basketball tournament!</font>

301
00:15:01,510 --> 00:15:02,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is bad.</font>

302
00:15:02,940 --> 00:15:03,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

303
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:09,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The winner of both the individual and 
group swimming competitions is Dorm 1.</i></font>

304
00:15:11,070 --> 00:15:13,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what's the overall ranking now?</font>

305
00:15:13,050 --> 00:15:14,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="12"><font color="#353436"><b>Overall Ranking Announcement</b></font></font></font></font>

306
00:15:16,430 --> 00:15:19,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right now, Dorm 2 is in last place.</font>

307
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:22,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we were so happy just now...</font>

308
00:15:22,340 --> 00:15:23,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those bastards.</font>

309
00:15:23,740 --> 00:15:26,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not allowed to compete
in sporting events you're on the team for,</font>

310
00:15:26,940 --> 00:15:30,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so they had their guys quit 
the swim team temporarily.</font>

311
00:15:30,070 --> 00:15:31,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's so dirty.</font>

312
00:15:31,760 --> 00:15:33,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's call it what it is: strategy.</font>

313
00:15:33,650 --> 00:15:34,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Strategy, I say!</font>

314
00:15:35,700 --> 00:15:37,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tennoji...</font>

315
00:15:38,290 --> 00:15:40,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You could try using your head for once.</font>

316
00:15:40,640 --> 00:15:41,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

317
00:15:41,770 --> 00:15:44,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got a lot of nerve coming 
in here to talk trash</font>

318
00:15:44,140 --> 00:15:47,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when you're using all kinds 
of dirty tricks to win!</font>

319
00:15:47,500 --> 00:15:48,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're too soft!</font>

320
00:15:48,540 --> 00:15:51,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All is fair in love and war!</font>

321
00:15:52,020 --> 00:15:54,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll send you packing 
in the chicken fight,</font>

322
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:55,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you big-mouth brat.</font>

323
00:15:55,470 --> 00:15:57,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't wait to see you try!</font>

324
00:16:00,770 --> 00:16:02,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the...?</font>

325
00:16:02,010 --> 00:16:03,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't get mixed up with Kujo.</font>

326
00:16:04,820 --> 00:16:07,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's talk that some punk
tried to mess with him.</font>

327
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He dislocated the dude's arm.</font>

328
00:16:09,480 --> 00:16:12,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say he didn't even blink.</font>

329
00:16:16,380 --> 00:16:20,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Paging all volleyball players.
Please gather up.</i></font>

330
00:16:16,380 --> 00:16:20,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Keep calm, keep calm, keep calm!</i></font>

331
00:16:20,340 --> 00:16:21,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Okay!</i></font>

332
00:16:21,250 --> 00:16:23,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on. They're calling for you guys.</font>

333
00:16:23,760 --> 00:16:27,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right. Now we've got to pay 
them back in volleyball,</font>

334
00:16:27,070 --> 00:16:28,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">no matter the cost!</font>

335
00:16:28,800 --> 00:16:30,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go, maggots!</font>

336
00:16:30,340 --> 00:16:31,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

337
00:16:38,150 --> 00:16:39,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We lost...</font>

338
00:16:39,270 --> 00:16:41,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're out in the first round...</font>

339
00:16:50,820 --> 00:16:54,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It would appear some of our dorm
 members have behaved roughly.</font>

340
00:16:56,380 --> 00:16:57,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you stand?</font>

341
00:16:57,820 --> 00:17:02,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am the RA of Dorm 3, Oscar M. Himejima.</font>

342
00:17:02,330 --> 00:17:04,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're Dorm 3's...</font>

343
00:17:04,830 --> 00:17:06,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You poor thing.</font>

344
00:17:07,280 --> 00:17:11,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A beautiful kid like you
 stuck in that squalid place...</font>

345
00:17:11,500 --> 00:17:12,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

346
00:17:12,590 --> 00:17:14,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Transfer over into Dorm 3.</font>

347
00:17:14,640 --> 00:17:16,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You will want for nothing. Well?</font>

348
00:17:16,820 --> 00:17:18,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine, thanks...</font>

349
00:17:18,590 --> 00:17:21,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Get yer filthy meathooks off of him!</font>

350
00:17:23,180 --> 00:17:26,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How dare you, you uncivilized caveman?!</font>

351
00:17:26,090 --> 00:17:28,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's an insult to cavemen.</font>

352
00:17:28,600 --> 00:17:31,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You tryin' to piss me off, Izumi?</font>

353
00:17:31,040 --> 00:17:32,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who're you even fooling?!</font>

354
00:17:32,280 --> 00:17:33,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We all know your name is Masao!</font>

355
00:17:32,820 --> 00:17:34,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="14">{\an9}<font color="#1b1b1d"><b>Real name
<font size="20">Himejima Masao</font></b></font></font></font></font>

356
00:17:36,100 --> 00:17:38,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Then what's with "Oscar"?</font>

357
00:17:39,760 --> 00:17:41,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Till we meet again, little kitten!</font>

358
00:17:41,560 --> 00:17:43,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Adieu!</font>

359
00:17:43,000 --> 00:17:44,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get outta here already!</font>

360
00:17:45,850 --> 00:17:48,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, he's really overdoing it.</font>

361
00:17:48,480 --> 00:17:50,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's nearsighted real bad.</font>

362
00:17:50,600 --> 00:17:52,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're sure in the know.</font>

363
00:17:52,380 --> 00:17:56,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's president of the theater club
and has apparently won some fancy awards.</font>

364
00:17:56,400 --> 00:17:59,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goes around saying his great 
grandpa's German or some bull.</font>

365
00:17:59,130 --> 00:18:01,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like, dude, gimme a break.</font>

366
00:18:01,010 --> 00:18:02,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I see.</font>

367
00:18:02,720 --> 00:18:04,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's a bit of an oddball.</font>

368
00:18:04,390 --> 00:18:05,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="16"><font color="#8b7d91">Dorm 1\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDorm 2\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDorm 3</font></font></font></font>

369
00:18:05,850 --> 00:18:09,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After the morning events, 
our dorm is in last place.</font>

370
00:18:09,360 --> 00:18:12,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess Dorm 1 really is going hard.</font>

371
00:18:12,320 --> 00:18:13,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess so.</font>

372
00:18:13,570 --> 00:18:15,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enough with the long faces.</font>

373
00:18:15,080 --> 00:18:17,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No use crying over spilled milk.</font>

374
00:18:19,940 --> 00:18:23,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa, Nanba-senpai, you look so cool!</font>

375
00:18:24,240 --> 00:18:25,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you up to?</font>

376
00:18:25,760 --> 00:18:29,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to be in the upcoming 
cheer squad competition.</font>

377
00:18:29,310 --> 00:18:31,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The RAs wear white uniforms.</font>

378
00:18:31,130 --> 00:18:34,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How do you score the cheer squad event?</font>

379
00:18:34,500 --> 00:18:37,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's decided by Osaka faculty and staff.</font>

380
00:18:37,770 --> 00:18:40,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The students would just
 vote for their own dorms.</font>

381
00:18:40,330 --> 00:18:42,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I see.</font>

382
00:18:42,640 --> 00:18:43,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="16"><font color="#8b7d91">Dorm 1\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDorm 2\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDorm 3</font></font></font></font>

383
00:18:43,640 --> 00:18:46,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dorm 1 has a pretty big lead.</font>

384
00:18:46,350 --> 00:18:47,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're sorry.</font>

385
00:18:47,980 --> 00:18:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ashiya.</font>

386
00:18:48,750 --> 00:18:49,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yeah?</font>

387
00:18:50,030 --> 00:18:54,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd better beat Dorm 1 
in the 500-meter relay.</font>

388
00:18:54,080 --> 00:18:55,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

389
00:18:55,420 --> 00:18:57,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we lose that, we're done for.</font>

390
00:18:57,830 --> 00:18:58,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can do it, right?</font>

391
00:18:59,800 --> 00:19:00,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

392
00:19:15,910 --> 00:19:20,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May the cherry trees here
 blossom abundantly!</font>

393
00:19:21,430 --> 00:19:25,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As we brave the mountain air upon us!</font>

394
00:19:27,810 --> 00:19:31,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Show us your smoldering spirits!</font>

395
00:19:33,580 --> 00:19:38,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is our Osaka!</font>

396
00:19:43,320 --> 00:19:44,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How cool!</font>

397
00:19:44,850 --> 00:19:48,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our RA really knows how to bring it.</font>

398
00:19:48,330 --> 00:19:51,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so glad I got to witness 
this, Nanba-senpai!</font>

399
00:19:51,330 --> 00:19:53,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="16"><font color="#8b7d91">Dorm 1\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDorm 2\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDorm 3</font></font></font></font>

400
00:19:52,090 --> 00:19:53,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The results are in!</i></font>

401
00:19:55,860 --> 00:19:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i><font face="Arial"><font size="16"><font color="#8b7d91">Dorm 1\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDorm 2\h\h\h\h\h\h\hDorm 3</font></font></font></i></font>

402
00:19:57,340 --> 00:20:00,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, we got the most votes!</font>

403
00:20:00,850 --> 00:20:02,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your aura is golden.</font>

404
00:20:02,950 --> 00:20:04,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice!</font>

405
00:20:04,140 --> 00:20:05,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're a lot closer than before!</font>

406
00:20:07,920 --> 00:20:09,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sorry!</font>

407
00:20:09,050 --> 00:20:11,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm still behaving like I'm in America—</font>

408
00:20:13,090 --> 00:20:14,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Wh-What?!</font>

409
00:20:14,350 --> 00:20:16,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Payback for last time.</font>

410
00:20:16,610 --> 00:20:19,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wh-What happened last time?!</i></font>

411
00:20:19,690 --> 00:20:20,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuki!</font>

412
00:20:20,720 --> 00:20:22,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's get to the 500-meter relay!</font>

413
00:20:23,300 --> 00:20:24,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Already?</font>

414
00:20:24,920 --> 00:20:26,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wasn't expecting that.</i></font>

415
00:20:26,520 --> 00:20:28,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My heart is still pounding.</i></font>

416
00:20:29,540 --> 00:20:32,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And now, on to the climactic event:</i></font>

417
00:20:32,100 --> 00:20:34,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the 500-meter relay featuring 
all three grades!</i></font>

418
00:20:40,360 --> 00:20:41,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mizuki!</font>

419
00:20:41,300 --> 00:20:44,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The baton has just been passed 
to their anchor runner, Ashiya.</i></font>

420
00:20:45,510 --> 00:20:47,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He certainly is fast!</i></font>

421
00:20:49,760 --> 00:20:51,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Dorm 2 team has done it!</i></font>

422
00:20:51,710 --> 00:20:53,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They finish first!</i></font>

423
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:54,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Second is Dorm 1.</i></font>

424
00:20:54,590 --> 00:20:56,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And third, Dorm 3.</i></font>

425
00:20:56,900 --> 00:20:58,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good one, Ashiya!</font>

426
00:21:00,890 --> 00:21:02,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You did good too, Nakatsu.</font>

427
00:21:02,520 --> 00:21:04,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What, I'm an afterthought?</font>

428
00:21:04,390 --> 00:21:06,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, why did you bring that?</font>

429
00:21:06,280 --> 00:21:07,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh...</font>

430
00:21:09,530 --> 00:21:12,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The events are finished, 
so we already cleaned up.</font>

431
00:21:13,390 --> 00:21:15,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take that back to the storeroom.</font>

432
00:21:15,350 --> 00:21:16,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right!</font>

433
00:21:17,790 --> 00:21:20,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's see... Where's the storeroom again?</font>

434
00:21:23,320 --> 00:21:24,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nanba-senpai?</font>

435
00:21:24,680 --> 00:21:25,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Senpai!</font>

436
00:21:25,530 --> 00:21:26,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's the store—</font>

437
00:21:32,660 --> 00:21:33,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's going on here?</i></font>

438
00:21:34,240 --> 00:21:36,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is he seriously trying to pick up 
some girl right now?</i></font>

439
00:21:50,520 --> 00:21:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wonder if he's got an older girlfriend.</i></font>

440
00:21:52,950 --> 00:21:54,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She was crying.</i></font>

441
00:21:54,880 --> 00:21:57,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Did he break up with her?</i></font>

442
00:21:57,810 --> 00:22:01,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm doing that thing again where I 
stick my nose into people's business!</i></font>

443
00:22:01,460 --> 00:22:03,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I need to hurry up and take this back.</i></font>

444
00:22:04,460 --> 00:22:07,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wasn't expecting him to be that 
good in the 500-meter relay.</font>

445
00:22:07,970 --> 00:22:12,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><b><font size="14"><font color="#353336">Crush Ashiya Mizuki in the chicken fight</font></font></b></font></font>

446
00:22:08,410 --> 00:22:12,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can bet they'll put him in the
 2,000-meter relay on the last day.</font>

447
00:23:45,730 --> 00:23:50,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The key to our team's victory is none 
other than yours truly, Oscar M. Himejima!</font>

448
00:23:50,010 --> 00:23:53,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These beautiful cheers will become 
hymns of praise for my beauty!</font>

449
00:23:53,540 --> 00:23:55,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Praise me!</font>

450
00:23:55,660 --> 00:23:58,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's just Masao cheering for Masao!</font>

451
00:23:58,010 --> 00:23:59,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="20"><font face="Impact"><font color="#c7377d">Next Time</font></font></font></font>

452
00:23:58,010 --> 00:23:59,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Impact">{\an8}<font color="#c7377d">Nanba-Senpai?</font></font></font>

